{"tid":1760803,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"支那考慮禁止起草人權民主法案的人入境","createTime":"2019-11-28T12:54:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-28T23:38:35.000Z","uid":79563,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"550e735fba06a220b5fe550c7f8cbbaf61a9b326","tid":1760803,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T12:54:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1495003-20191128.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1495003-20191128.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=gSA20A4kU26EBUHkB65AtHfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=a205b01f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1495003-20191128.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=612f091a\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1495003-20191128.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普簽署《香港人權與民主法案》，表示是出於對中國國家主席習近平與香港人民的尊重。外交部副部長樂玉成召見美國駐華大使布蘭斯塔德，提出嚴正交涉及強烈抗議，揚言會予以堅決反制。<br />\n<br />\n內地《環球時報》總編輯胡錫進在社交網站Twitter表示，據他理解，出於對特朗普、美國及美國人民的尊重，中國正考慮將法案的起草人，列入禁止入境名單，禁止他們進入中國大陸、香港及澳門。<br />\n<br />\n胡錫進無詳細說明措施細節，亦無透露是如何獲得這個消息。胡錫進較早前貼文，指如果美方使用法案制裁親建制人士，相信北京會採取行動，對付華盛頓在香港的代理人，強調中國不容許香港激進反對派，大肆與美國勾結"},{"pid":"45675a33582dbdd06ebc1314f0fe0a1de27797fc","tid":1760803,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T12:56:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6704064c96a280b7857964c56e8bcc46111ff68f","tid":1760803,"uid":321837,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T12:59:48.000Z","msg":"當勞侵負責簽,簽完仲好多嘢講.點計? 連紫禁城都入埋喇............"},{"pid":"28fd8179c6e37a31e17d725b8764064858d72fec","tid":1760803,"uid":245849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T12:59:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9eced13dfed74d1c9b2d453f152047e579076ebd","tid":1760803,"uid":